github.com/townsendmerino/wgpu
===============================

This package vendors prebuilt static libraries and C headers from wgpu-native,
pinned to release v29.0.0.0 (https://github.com/gfx-rs/wgpu-native).

Vendored blobs:
  lib/<goos>/<goarch>/libwgpu_native.a   prebuilt static library
  lib/webgpu.h                           header from the v29.0.0.0 release archive
  lib/wgpu.h                             header from the v29.0.0.0 release archive

These are taken verbatim from the v29.0.0.0 release archives so that the headers
match the linked library ABI exactly.

